title: [Laphrael's General Store]
description: Beneath a varnished golden oak ceiling, a cork bulletin board hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A lacquered wooden shelf and a gilded maple table sit in opposite corners while a pile of wooden shoe lasts rests on a polished oak floor.

Beneath a varnished golden oak ceiling, a cork bulletin board hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A set of carved felwood shelves and a heavy lead glass display case sit in opposite corners while a pile of wooden shoe lasts rests on a polished oak floor.
